WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Alpine plants show us natural mathematics!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
Mountain flowers grow in patterns we can count and measure.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Plant heights, leaf shapes, and growth rates create data.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Scientists use numbers to study how plants adapt to mountains.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Let's discover the maths in mountain ecosystems!